    source: CORTEX_STEP_SOURCE_USER_EXPLICIT
  }
  user_input {
    user_response: "Create a premium cannabis lifestyle e-commerce website for SATIVA YARD, based in Johannesburg, South Africa.\n\nIMPORTANT:\n\nBefore generating the website, create and display FIVE completely different homepage theme concepts for approval.\n\nEach concept must include:\n\n* Homepage mockup\n* Color palette\n* Typography selection\n* Navigation style\n* Hero section design\n* Product card style\n* Overall visual direction\n\nTheme Option 1:\nModern Cannabis Dispensary\n\nTheme Option 2:\nPremium Wellness & Lifestyle\n\nTheme Option 3:\nOrganic Botanical Store\n\nTheme Option 4:\nLuxury Cannabis Boutique\n\nTheme Option 5:\nModern South African Cannabis Brand\n\nAfter presenting all 5 options, recommend the strongest option for customer trust, sales conversion, and premium branding.\n\n================================================\n\nDESIGN DIRECTION\n\nDO NOT use a dark website.\n\nDO NOT use black backgrounds.\n\nDO NOT create a nightclub or underground cannabis aesthetic.\n\nThe website must feel:\n\nBright\n\nFresh\n\nModern\n\nProfessional\n\nPremium\n\nWelcoming\n\nTrustworthy\n\nNatural\n\nHigh-End\n\nClean\n\nUse plenty of:\n\nWhite backgrounds\n\nSoft green gradients\n\nNatural green accents\n\nBotanical elements\n\nModern cards\n\nRounded corners\n\nGlassmorphism effects\n\nSoft shadows\n\nClean layouts\n\nLots of whitespace\n\nThe website should look similar to a premium wellness brand, Apple-level clean design, modern online dispensary, or premium organic retail store.\n\n================================================\n\nPRIMARY COLORS\n\nWhite\n\nForest Green\n\nEmerald Green\n\nLime Green accents\n\nSoft Sage Green\n\nLight Grey\n\n================================================\n\nAVOID\n\nDark Black Themes\n\nHeavy Grunge Effects\n\nOverly Smokey Designs\n\nGangster Style Branding\n\nCluttered Layouts\n\nOld Cannabis Leaf Patterns Everywhere\n\n================================================\n\nBRAND INFORMATION\n\nBusiness Name:\n\nSATIVA YARD\n\nLocation:\n\nJohannesburg, South Africa\n\nIndustry:\n\nCannabis Lifestyle\nCannabis Products\nCannabis Wellness\nCannabis Education\n\nBrand Personality:\n\nProfessional\n\nTrusted\n\nPremium\n\nEducational\n\nModern\n\nClean\n\nInnovative\n\nEstablished\n\n================================================\n\nWEBSITE STRUCTURE\n\n1. Home Page\n\n2. About Us Page\n\n3. Products Page\n\n4. Contact Page\n\n================================================\n\nHOME PAGE\n\nSECTION 1\n\nHero Banner\n\nLarge premium lifestyle imagery.\n\nHeadline:\n\nJohannesburg\'s Premium Cannabis Lifestyle Destination\n\nSubheadline:\n\nExplore premium cannabis products, wellness solutions, accessories and education from one of Johannesburg\'s most trusted cannabis lifestyle brands.\n\nButtons:\n\nShop Products\n\nContact Us\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 2\n\nAbout Sativa Yard\n\nProfessional company introduction.\n\nCreate a premium corporate presentation that feels like an established business with years of experience.\n\nInclude:\n\nMission\n\nVision\n\nValues\n\nCustomer Commitment\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 3\n\nWhy Choose Sativa Yard\n\nPremium Product Selection\n\nQuality Assurance\n\nExpert Guidance\n\nFast WhatsApp Ordering\n\nCustomer Education\n\nProfessional Support\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 4\n\nFeatured Products\n\nDisplay products in modern e-commerce cards.\n\nInclude:\n\nProduct Image\n\nProduct Name\n\nPrice\n\nCategory\n\nAdd To Cart\n\nView Product\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 5\n\nCannabis Education\n\nCreate a modern educational section explaining:\n\nSativa\n\nIndica\n\nHybrid\n\nInclude professional illustrations and modern infographics.\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 6\n\nCustomer Testimonials\n\nModern review cards.\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 7\n\nCall To Action\n\nReady To Explore Premium Cannabis Products?\n\nShop Now\n\nChat On WhatsApp\n\n================================================\n\nABOUT US PAGE\n\nCompany Story\n\nMission\n\nVision\n\nValues\n\nCannabis Education\n\nCommunity Commitment\n\nQuality Standards\n\nProfessional imagery throughout.\n\n================================================\n\nPRODUCTS PAGE\n\nCategories:\n\nCannabis Flower\n\nPre-Rolls\n\nEdibles\n\nConcentrates\n\nVapes\n\nAccessories\n\nLifestyle Products\n\nBranded Merchandise\n\n================================================\n\nPRODUCT FEATURES\n\nEach product must include:\n\nProduct Image\n\nProduct Name\n\nDescription\n\nCategory\n\nPrice\n\nWeight\n\nAvailability\n\nSKU\n\nStrain Type\n\nAdd To Cart\n\n================================================\n\nFILTERS\n\nSearch Products\n\nFilter By Category\n\nFilter By Price\n\nFilter By Strain\n\nSort By Popularity\n\n================================================\n\nSHOPPING CART\n\nAdd To Cart\n\nUpdate Quantities\n\nRemove Products\n\nCart Summary\n\nTotal Price Calculation\n\n================================================\n\nWHATSAPP CHECKOUT\n\nCustomer adds products to cart.\n\nCustomer clicks:\n\nProceed To WhatsApp Order\n\nGenerate:\n\nHello Sativa Yard,\n\nI would like to place an order.\n\nProducts:\n\n[Product Name]\n\n[Quantity]\n\n[Price]\n\nTotal:\n\nR XXXX\n\nCustomer Name:\n\nCustomer Number:\n\nThank you.\n\nAutomatically open WhatsApp with the completed order.\n\n================================================\n\nCONTACT PAGE\n\nContact Information\n\nWhatsApp Number\n\nPhone Number\n\nEmail Address\n\nBusiness Address\n\nBusiness Hours\n\nGoogle Maps\n\nContact Form\n\nSocial Media Links\n\nFacebook\n\nInstagram\n\nTikTok\n\nWhatsApp\n\n================================================\n\nTECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS\n\nResponsive Design\n\nMobile First\n\nSEO Optimized\n\nFast Loading\n\nModern UI/UX\n\nTailwind CSS\n\nHTML5\n\nJavaScript\n\nProduct Search\n\nProduct Filters\n\nWhatsApp Checkout\n\nGoogle Maps Integration\n\nNewsletter Signup\n\nAnalytics Ready\n\nSticky Navigation\n\nProfessional Footer\n\nPremium Animations\n\n================================================\n\nFINAL GOAL\n\nThe website must feel like the most professional cannabis lifestyle store in Johannesburg.\n\nThe design should be bright, clean, modern, premium, trustworthy, conversion-focused, and visually comparable to leading wellness, lifestyle, and e-commerce brands rather than traditional dark cannabis websites.\n"
    items {
      text: "Create a premium cannabis lifestyle e-commerce website for SATIVA YARD, based in Johannesburg, South Africa.\n\nIMPORTANT:\n\nBefore generating the website, create and display FIVE completely different homepage theme concepts for approval.\n\nEach concept must include:\n\n* Homepage mockup\n* Color palette\n* Typography selection\n* Navigation style\n* Hero section design\n* Product card style\n* Overall visual direction\n\nTheme Option 1:\nModern Cannabis Dispensary\n\nTheme Option 2:\nPremium Wellness & Lifestyle\n\nTheme Option 3:\nOrganic Botanical Store\n\nTheme Option 4:\nLuxury Cannabis Boutique\n\nTheme Option 5:\nModern South African Cannabis Brand\n\nAfter presenting all 5 options, recommend the strongest option for customer trust, sales conversion, and premium branding.\n\n================================================\n\nDESIGN DIRECTION\n\nDO NOT use a dark website.\n\nDO NOT use black backgrounds.\n\nDO NOT create a nightclub or underground cannabis aesthetic.\n\nThe website must feel:\n\nBright\n\nFresh\n\nModern\n\nProfessional\n\nPremium\n\nWelcoming\n\nTrustworthy\n\nNatural\n\nHigh-End\n\nClean\n\nUse plenty of:\n\nWhite backgrounds\n\nSoft green gradients\n\nNatural green accents\n\nBotanical elements\n\nModern cards\n\nRounded corners\n\nGlassmorphism effects\n\nSoft shadows\n\nClean layouts\n\nLots of whitespace\n\nThe website should look similar to a premium wellness brand, Apple-level clean design, modern online dispensary, or premium organic retail store.\n\n================================================\n\nPRIMARY COLORS\n\nWhite\n\nForest Green\n\nEmerald Green\n\nLime Green accents\n\nSoft Sage Green\n\nLight Grey\n\n================================================\n\nAVOID\n\nDark Black Themes\n\nHeavy Grunge Effects\n\nOverly Smokey Designs\n\nGangster Style Branding\n\nCluttered Layouts\n\nOld Cannabis Leaf Patterns Everywhere\n\n================================================\n\nBRAND INFORMATION\n\nBusiness Name:\n\nSATIVA YARD\n\nLocation:\n\nJohannesburg, South Africa\n\nIndustry:\n\nCannabis Lifestyle\nCannabis Products\nCannabis Wellness\nCannabis Education\n\nBrand Personality:\n\nProfessional\n\nTrusted\n\nPremium\n\nEducational\n\nModern\n\nClean\n\nInnovative\n\nEstablished\n\n================================================\n\nWEBSITE STRUCTURE\n\n1. Home Page\n\n2. About Us Page\n\n3. Products Page\n\n4. Contact Page\n\n================================================\n\nHOME PAGE\n\nSECTION 1\n\nHero Banner\n\nLarge premium lifestyle imagery.\n\nHeadline:\n\nJohannesburg\'s Premium Cannabis Lifestyle Destination\n\nSubheadline:\n\nExplore premium cannabis products, wellness solutions, accessories and education from one of Johannesburg\'s most trusted cannabis lifestyle brands.\n\nButtons:\n\nShop Products\n\nContact Us\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 2\n\nAbout Sativa Yard\n\nProfessional company introduction.\n\nCreate a premium corporate presentation that feels like an established business with years of experience.\n\nInclude:\n\nMission\n\nVision\n\nValues\n\nCustomer Commitment\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 3\n\nWhy Choose Sativa Yard\n\nPremium Product Selection\n\nQuality Assurance\n\nExpert Guidance\n\nFast WhatsApp Ordering\n\nCustomer Education\n\nProfessional Support\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 4\n\nFeatured Products\n\nDisplay products in modern e-commerce cards.\n\nInclude:\n\nProduct Image\n\nProduct Name\n\nPrice\n\nCategory\n\nAdd To Cart\n\nView Product\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 5\n\nCannabis Education\n\nCreate a modern educational section explaining:\n\nSativa\n\nIndica\n\nHybrid\n\nInclude professional illustrations and modern infographics.\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 6\n\nCustomer Testimonials\n\nModern review cards.\n\n================================================\n\nSECTION 7\n\nCall To Action\n\nReady To Explore Premium Cannabis Products?\n\nShop Now\n\nChat On WhatsApp\n\n================================================\n\nABOUT US PAGE\n\nCompany Story\n\nMission\n\nVision\n\nValues\n\nCannabis Education\n\nCommunity Commitment\n\nQuality Standards\n\nProfessional imagery throughout.\n\n================================================\n\nPRODUCTS PAGE\n\nCategories:\n\nCannabis Flower\n\nPre-Rolls\n\nEdibles\n\nConcentrates\n\nVapes\n\nAccessories\n\nLifestyle Products\n\nBranded Merchandise\n\n================================================\n\nPRODUCT FEATURES\n\nEach product must include:\n\nProduct Image\n\nProduct Name\n\nDescription\n\nCategory\n\nPrice\n\nWeight\n\nAvailability\n\nSKU\n\nStrain Type\n\nAdd To Cart\n\n================================================\n\nFILTERS\n\nSearch Products\n\nFilter By Category\n\nFilter By Price\n\nFilter By Strain\n\nSort By Popularity\n\n================================================\n\nSHOPPING CART\n\nAdd To Cart\n\nUpdate Quantities\n\nRemove Products\n\nCart Summary\n\nTotal Price Calculation\n\n================================================\n\nWHATSAPP CHECKOUT\n\nCustomer adds products to cart.\n\nCustomer clicks:\n\nProceed To WhatsApp Order\n\nGenerate:\n\nHello Sativa Yard,\n\nI would like to place an order.\n\nProducts:\n\n[Product Name]\n\n[Quantity]\n\n[Price]\n\nTotal:\n\nR XXXX\n\nCustomer Name:\n\nCustomer Number:\n\nThank you.\n\nAutomatically open WhatsApp with the completed order.\n\n================================================\n\nCONTACT PAGE\n\nContact Information\n\nWhatsApp Number\n\nPhone Number\n\nEmail Address\n\nBusiness Address\n\nBusiness Hours\n\nGoogle Maps\n\nContact Form\n\nSocial Media Links\n\nFacebook\n\nInstagram\n\nTikTok\n\nWhatsApp\n\n================================================\n\nTECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS\n\nResponsive Design\n\nMobile First\n\nSEO Optimized\n\nFast Loading\n\nModern UI/UX\n\nTailwind CSS\n\nHTML5\n\nJavaScript\n\nProduct Search\n\nProduct Filters\n\nWhatsApp Checkout\n\nGoogle Maps Integration\n\nNewsletter Signup\n\nAnalytics Ready\n\nSticky Navigation\n\nProfessional Footer\n\nPremium Animations\n\n================================================\n\nFINAL GOAL\n\nThe website must feel like the most professional cannabis lifestyle store in Johannesburg.\n\nThe design should be bright, clean, modern, premium, trustworthy, conversion-focused, and visually comparable to leading wellness, lifestyle, and e-commerce brands rather than traditional dark cannabis websites.\n"
