n the cart. Now, I have implemented `addToCart`, which handles existing or new products, and I am starting the implementation for `removeFromCart` and `updateQuantity`.\n\n\n**Implementing Cart Updates**\n\nI\'ve completed the implementation of `updateQuantity` within the cart context, ensuring quantities are adjusted and zero quantities trigger removal.  I\'ve finalized `cartTotal` and `cartItemCount` calculations and confirmed their use in providing cart summaries. I\'m now working to connect this context to my application\'s component tree. Finally, I\'m going to update `index.css` for typography and basic variables.\n\n\n"
