  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Editorial Aesthetic\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Editorial Aesthetic\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-gray-50 flex flex-col font-sans overflow-hidden text-emerald-900\\\">\\n  <!-- Top Navigation -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"h-20 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-emerald-100 px-12 flex items-center justify-between sticky top-0 z-50\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-8\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-emerald-800\\\">SATIVA YARD</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"hidden lg:flex gap-6 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-700/70\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"text-emerald-900\\\">Shop</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\">Wellness</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\">Education</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\">About</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-emerald-50 rounded-full text-emerald-700 text-xs font-bold border border-emerald-100\\\">\\n        JOHANNESBURG, SA\\n      </div>\\n      <button class=\\\"p-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 text-white\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"Option 3: 16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z\\\"></path></svg>\\n      </button>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex gap-8 p-8 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Column: Hero & Mission -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-3/5 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[40px] p-10 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center shadow-sm border border-emerald-50\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-emerald-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs mb-4\\\">Premium Lifestyle</span>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-6xl font-extrabold leading-[0.9] tracking-tight mb-6\\\">\\n          Johannesburg\'s Premium <br/><span class=\\\"text-emerald-700\\\">Cannabis Destination.</span>\\n        </h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-emerald-800/70 text-lg max-w-md leading-relaxed mb-8\\\">\\n          Explore premium cannabis products, wellness solutions, and expert education from SA\'s most trusted lifestyle brand.\\n        </p>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 bg-emerald-700 text-white rounded-2xl font-bold hover:bg-emerald-800 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-emerald-700/20\\\">Shop Products</button>\\n          <button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 bg-white border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-700 rounded-2xl font-bold\\\">Learn More</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"h-40 flex gap-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-emerald-100/50 rounded-[32px] p-6 border border-emerald-100 flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold\\\">!</div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Quality Assured</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-emerald-800 rounded-[32px] p-6 text-white flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-white/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-mono\\\">WA</div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">WhatsApp Checkout</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white rounded-[32px] p-6 border border-emerald-100 flex flex-col justify-between shadow-sm\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 font-bold\\\">+</div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Expert Education</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Column: Products & Education -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-2/5 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Featured Product Card -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[40px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-emerald-50 flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-6\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold\\\">Featured Collection</h3>\\n          <span class=\\\"px-3 py-1 bg-lime-100 text-lime-800 text-[10px] font-black rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Sativa Dom</span>\\n        </div>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-emerald-50/50 rounded-2xl mb-6 relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-10\\\">\\n            <svg class=\\\"w-32 h-32\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"currentColor\\\"><path d=\\\"M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z\\\"/></svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-100\\\">\\n             <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n               <div>\\n                 <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-800\\\">Highveld Gold Flower</p>\\n                 <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-emerald-600\\\">3.5g \342\200\242 Johannesburg Grown</p>\\n               </div>\\n               <p class=\\\"text-lg font-black text-emerald-900\\\">R 450</p>\\n             </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        \\n        <button class=\\\"w-full py-4 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 font-bold rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100\\\">View All Products</button>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Education Section -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-emerald-900 rounded-[40px] p-8 text-emerald-50\\\">\\n        <h4 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 text-emerald-400\\\">The Library</h4>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-lg font-serif italic mb-4\\\">\\\"Understanding Terpenes in the South African context...\\\"</p>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-800 border border-emerald-700\\\"></div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs opacity-70\\\">By Dr. K. Zulu, Lead Researcher</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Footer / Status Bar -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-12 bg-white border-t border-emerald-100 px-12 flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-600/60\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-8\\\">\\n      <span>Established 2021</span>\\n      <span>Certified Laboratory Testing</span>\\n      <span>Secure WhatsApp Payments</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-emerald-700\\\">Instagram</span>\\n      <span>Facebook</span>\\n      <span>LinkedIn</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Editorial Aesthetic\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Editorial Aesthetic\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-gray-50 flex flex-col font-sans overflow-hidden text-emerald-900\\\">\\n  <!-- Top Navigation -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"h-20 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-emerald-100 px-12 flex items-center justify-between sticky top-0 z-50\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-8\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-emerald-800\\\">SATIVA YARD</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"hidden lg:flex gap-6 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-700/70\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"text-emerald-900\\\">Shop</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\">Wellness</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\">Education</a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\">About</a>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-emerald-50 rounded-full text-emerald-700 text-xs font-bold border border-emerald-100\\\">\\n        JOHANNESBURG, SA\\n      </div>\\n      <button class=\\\"p-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 text-white\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"Option 3: 16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z\\\"></path></svg>\\n      </button>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex gap-8 p-8 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Column: Hero & Mission -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-3/5 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[40px] p-10 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center shadow-sm border border-emerald-50\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-emerald-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs mb-4\\\">Premium Lifestyle</span>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-6xl font-extrabold leading-[0.9] tracking-tight mb-6\\\">\\n          Johannesburg\'s Premium <br/><span class=\\\"text-emerald-700\\\">Cannabis Destination.</span>\\n        </h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-emerald-800/70 text-lg max-w-md leading-relaxed mb-8\\\">\\n          Explore premium cannabis products, wellness solutions, and expert education from SA\'s most trusted lifestyle brand.\\n        </p>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 bg-emerald-700 text-white rounded-2xl font-bold hover:bg-emerald-800 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-emerald-700/20\\\">Shop Products</button>\\n          <button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 bg-white border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-700 rounded-2xl font-bold\\\">Learn More</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"h-40 flex gap-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-emerald-100/50 rounded-[32px] p-6 border border-emerald-100 flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold\\\">!</div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Quality Assured</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-emerald-800 rounded-[32px] p-6 text-white flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-white/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-mono\\\">WA</div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">WhatsApp Checkout</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white rounded-[32px] p-6 border border-emerald-100 flex flex-col justify-between shadow-sm\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 font-bold\\\">+</div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Expert Education</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Column: Products & Education -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-2/5 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Featured Product Card -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[40px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-emerald-50 flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-6\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold\\\">Featured Collection</h3>\\n         